Here's a complete implementation of the Offline Unit Converter web app based on your specification. This solution includes:

Semantic HTML5 , modular CSS , and ES6+ JavaScript
Extensible architecture with decoupled conversion logic
LocalStorage for persistent history and dark mode
Validation , accessibility , and responsive design
Future-proof structure for easy enhancements

