ðŸš§ Suggested Future Enhancements
Add More Categories : Expand units.json with currency, data-size, or time.
Export History : Add CSV/JSON export button.
PWA Support : Register a service worker for offline installability.
Custom Unit Groups : Let users create custom unit groups (e.g., "favorites").
Real-Time Conversion : Debounce input for instant conversion feedback.
This implementation provides a clean, extensible foundation for future expansion while maintaining performance, accessibility, and usability across devices.
